    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>测试描述，你好啊探索者</p><h2 id="正式内容"><a href="#正式内容" class="headerlink" title="正式内容"></a>正式内容</h2><p>如果月亮还没来，那就先来个星星吧</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Explorer-Studio/Explorer-Studio.github.io@master/source/_posts/test/1.jpg" alt="星星"></p><h2 id="代码测试"><a href="#代码测试" class="headerlink" title="代码测试"></a>代码测试</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Test</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello World!&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="数学公式测试"><a href="#数学公式测试" class="headerlink" title="数学公式测试"></a>数学公式测试</h2><p>$$\sum_{i&#x3D;1}^{n}i &#x3D; \frac{n(n+1)}{2}$$</p><h2 id="表格测试"><a href="#表格测试" class="headerlink" title="表格测试"></a>表格测试</h2><table><thead><tr><th>姓名</th><th>年龄</th><th>性别</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>张三</td><td>20</td><td>男</td></tr><tr><td>李四</td><td>18</td><td>女</td></tr><tr><td>王五</td><td>22</td><td>男</td></tr><tr><td>赵六</td><td>19</td><td>女</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="图片测试"><a href="#图片测试" class="headerlink" title="图片测试"></a>图片测试</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Explorer-Studio/Explorer-Studio.github.io@master/source/_posts/test/2.jpg" alt="图片"></p><h2 id="视频测试"><a href="#视频测试" class="headerlink" title="视频测试"></a>视频测试</h2><p><video src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Explorer-Studio/Explorer-Studio.github.io@master/source/_posts/test/3.mp4" controls="controls" width="100%"></video></p><h2 id="音频测试"><a href="#音频测试" class="headerlink" title="音频测试"></a>音频测试</h2><p><audio src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Explorer-Studio/Explorer-Studio.github.io@master/source/_posts/test/4.mp3" controls="controls" width="100%"></audio></p><h2 id="链接测试"><a href="#链接测试" class="headerlink" title="链接测试"></a>链接测试</h2><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com/">百度</a></p><h2 id="引用测试"><a href="#引用测试" class="headerlink" title="引用测试"></a>引用测试</h2><blockquote><p>这是一个引用</p></blockquote><h2 id="代码块测试"><a href="#代码块测试" class="headerlink" title="代码块测试"></a>代码块测试</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Test</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;<br>        System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello World!&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="列表测试"><a href="#列表测试" class="headerlink" title="列表测试"></a>列表测试</h2><ul><li>列表1</li><li>列表2</li></ul><h2 id="分割线测试"><a href="#分割线测试" class="headerlink" title="分割线测试"></a>分割线测试</h2><hr><h2 id="表情包测试"><a href="#表情包测试" class="headerlink" title="表情包测试"></a>表情包测试</h2><p>:smile:</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
